      text_30: "ID document is the same as in “1”. Make sure photo/ID number is the same",
      text_31: "2.Notes on the “KYC Process”",
      text_32: "1) When the KYC process is unsuccessful then the reason is documented and a support ticket is created in the system. The ticket number along with an explanation is communicated back to the user.",
      text_33: "2) Once all proper documents are in our possession then the account gets approved.",
